ortunistic spanning corporate capital structures and leverages the knowledge of advent’s expert inhouse investment research team the new ucits fund will be asset class agnostic and will be optimally positioned to implement advent’s fundamental views under various market conditions “the expansion of our ucits product offerings into alternatives reinforces advent’s dedication to our european investors and reflects our proficiency in the alternatives space” said kris haber chief operating officer at advent capital “given the number of opportunities that currently exist in fixed income offering a credit ucit strategy is a natural step for advent and our clients” said robert gourlay managing director and head of european business development “the product is an excellent complement to our existing lineup and meets the significant credit demand we’ve had from our relationships in europe” odell lambroza has  years of industry experience the last  of which he’s spent at advent managing the global opportunity strategy and investing across the entire capital structure prior to advent he served as managing director of the convertible securities department at sg cowen and as vice president of structured equity derivative products asset swaps and convertible trading at merrill lynch matthew dundon joined advent from pine river capital where he coled a team of analysts focused on north american high yield distressed debt reorganized equities and messanine investing he was also involved in distressed and special opportunities in asia europe and the middle east prior to pine river he was head of research at gmp securities and has also practiced leveraged finance and securities law about advent capital management llc advent capital managementllcis a registered investment advisor founded in  advent manages approximately  billion in assets on behalf of corporations public pension plans foundations endowments and high net worth individuals globally across a variety of alternative investment traditional and closedend fundstrategiesthe firm’s proficiency in investing across the entire capital structure is driven by rigorous analysis and proprietary fundamental credit and equity research investment professionals collaborate globally to deliver compelling absolute and riskadjusted returns for its clients  as an irish undertakings for collective investments in transferable securities ucits compliant fund advent ucits funds plc may when officially approved by the central bank of ireland freely market and sell shares in the ucits throughout the european economic area where the ucits has complied with the notification and crossborder registration processes under the ucits directive or otherwise complies with applicable law advent ucits funds plc is currently not a recognised scheme for purposes of the financial services and markets act  and consequently its promotion either within or from the united kingdom is restricted by law this press release has therefore been prepared only for and is directed only at persons reasonably believed to be of a kind to whom an unauthorised person is permitted to communicate financial promotions pursuant to the financial services and markets act  financial promotion order  as amended the “fpo” such persons include a persons outside the united kingdom b persons having professional experience in matters relating to investments and c high net worth bodies corporate partnerships unincorporated associations trusts etc falling within article  of the fpo the services andor investments described herein are available only to such persons and persons of any other description may not rely on the information in this press release the ucits will not be offered or sold within the united states and is not available to us persons these materials are for informational and discussion purposes only this information should not be considered a solicitation or an offer to purchase shares of any advent sponsored or advised product or a solicitat